{"tid":435648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應跑手資料被盜　楊偉雄：過多網上登記或添風險","createTime":"2017-10-14T12:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T11:18:26.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"08e6d4ed58a293c86aa92954404ea12b4d4b84a2","tid":435648,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"多名跑手在網上以信用卡繳付渣打香港馬拉松報名費後，懷疑被人盜用資料交易，已報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長楊偉雄出席本台節目後表示，網上保安是比較複雜的問題，因為如在網上登記提供太多資料時，會牽涉盜用風險，因為現時互聯網盜用資料，可能是源於用家的手機或電腦。但他認為，香港在保安防禦方面工作做得很好。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉雄說，政府在數碼個人身分投入後，希望在兩年內令市民更安全享用不同電子政府服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fsjh.ilc.edu.tw/Resource/GIF/%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA%E5%95%8F%E8%99%9F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fsjh.ilc.edu.tw%2FResource%2FGIF%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%2599%259F.gif&h=cc476252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3042767da4bff77b90383059a5362da59e23930d","tid":435648,"uid":118132,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:54:11.000Z","msg":"點解要比個咩都唔識ge老野做局長, 真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"0c3e9c20446412ca8aea1a884f4654c52a9dbdc9","tid":435648,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要比個咩都唔識ge老野做局長, 真係得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n見過Steve jobs"},{"pid":"7d57405e2e87bdde56ed7e048f25979f2d9b6a27","tid":435648,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"數碼個人身分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"8be43ebe7d1e751f341c6efe31586a4104856818","tid":435648,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"陽痿熊屋企應該係石器時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdf6f066a6fade02ecc4035a3bc8df6f1ac18f8","tid":435648,"uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTi